column1: *sigh* Oh man, it's finally hittin' me...

Hang on, it's morning already? No wonder
I feel so beat...
Well, look who the cat dragged in.

So? How'd it go? Who was the Monarch? Was
it really a local? Find anything on Madicce—
We can tell you later... but now...

Oh! Looks like you guys had a real time in
there.
Wait here. I'll check out the route to the RV.
Will you be okay going alone?
I can watch your back for you.

You guys already pulled your weight and then
some. At least lemme help out now.
Thanks. I'll be in touch when I get a quick look.

Now that I think about it, we just took a boat
trip, went swimming, cooked a whole feast...
and then dove straight into a Jail.
At least the first half was a lot of fun.

Not only that, we learned quite a bit
from the Jail.

That voice, though... Who do you think that
was?

All I know is they're a real asshole, copyin'
Sophia's voice an' everything.

You're all-clear to come back to the RV.
I haven't seen a single local so far.

I can't tell if you guys really pulled it off or not,
but at least the coast is clear.

We returned to the RV for
some much-needed rest...
